2007-08-04 12:22 dangelo
	* configure.in, m4/acx_pthread.m4 m4/ax_check_gl.m4,
	  m4/ax_check_glu.m4, m4/ax_check_glut.m4: proper
	  detection of OpenGL and related libraries on OSX
	  (JD Smith)
	  
	* src/anneal.h: isnan doesn't work on OSX, use std::isnan instead
	  (JD Smith)
	  
	* src/gpu.h, src/gpu.cc, src/enblend.cc: call glutInit(), use 0.0
	  instead of 0.0f in gpu code (JD Smith, Edouard Gomez, Pete Woods)
	  
